title: Grateful Dead Live at Giants Stadium on 1993-06-05
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi DR-2 > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > R8Brain > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 Tagged
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Wang Dang Doodle, Peggy-O, Eternity, Candyman, The Music Never Stopped > Easy Answers^> The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Way To Go Home, Crazy Fingers-> Estimated Prophet-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> One More Saturday Night, E: Box Of Rain

Sting opened
^Easy Answers, Bobby debut in the middle of Music Never Stopped !!
